  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installasjon av Kactivities</title>

    <para>Installer <application>Kactivities</application> ved å kjøre følgende
    kommandoer:</para>

<!-- Nothing in sysconfdir here, too -->
<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir;   \
      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release           \
      -DCMAKE_MINIMUM_REQUIRED_VERSION=3.0 \
      -Wno-dev .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Denne pakken sender ikke en standard testpakke.</para>

    <para>Nå, som <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> bruker:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

